data.description: Welcome to this meticulously rebuilt Multi-Family Home, Located in a prime spot adjacent to RIC, with ample parking including a 2-car garage and a sizable storage building.    This home has been thoughtfully renovated, offering a fresh layout that maximizes space and functionality. The kitchens have been revitalized with new appliances. With turn-key efficiency, this property promises instant returns, making it an ideal investment opportunity. Unit 1 offers 2 generous sized bedrooms a fireplace, sliders to a cozy porch overlooking the private back yard and a full basement with washer and dryer. Unit 2 has a tenant in place through November.     Not just for investors, this home caters to those seeking a comfortable retreat. Enjoy the luxury of central air during the warmer months, complemented by a newer roof and low-maintenance vinyl siding. Step outside to discover a vast, private rear yard complete with a fireplace, perfect for outdoor gatherings. Adding to its allure, solar panels have been installed, providing an amazing reduction in electrical costs. Embrace sustainability while enjoying significant savings on utility bills. Underground sprinkler systems were installed recently. Utilities include one gas meter, and one electrical meter. Assumable Mortgage at 3.375 fixed rate for qualified buyers.    Experience the beauty and functionality of this home by stopping by the open house or by scheduling a private showing. Don't miss your chance to make this home your own!
